des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your “BRIGHTLUX”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “BRIGHTLUX” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “BRIGHTLUX” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “BRIGHTLUX” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “BRIGHTLUX” skill, and you'll be navigated to “BRIGHTLUX” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the light.”
“Alexa, turn off the light.”
“Alexa, set the light to 50%.”
“Alexa, set the light to 100%.”
“Alexa, dim the light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set the light to blue."
"Alexa, set the light to cool white."
"Alexa, set the light to warm white."
"Alexa, set the light to soft white."
"Alexa, set the light all the way up." 
"Alexa, set the light to the brightest mode."
